<i>adverb</i>: 완곡히 [완ː고키], 넌지시 [넌지시] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>완곡히 [완ː고키]</dt><br>
<dd>euphemistically; indirectly</dd><br>
<dd>듣는 사람의 기분이 상하지 않도록 말하는 투가 부드럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of speaking tactfully so that the listener will not be hurt.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>넌지시 [넌지시]</dt><br>
<dd>obliquely; indirectly</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 은근히.</dd><br>
<dd>By implication so that one's intention is not known directly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>